      "description": "This E46 M3 represents a superlative example of the legendary S54 platform. The high-revving 3.2L inline-six features a meticulously maintained Double VANOS system and crisp individual throttle body response. Power is delivered through a precise Getrag 6-speed manual to the rear wheels via the M Variable Differential Lock. The chassis is structurally sound with no evidence of subframe fatigue, and the suspension geometry remains factory-spec with all bushings and mounts in pristine order. A concours-level specimen for the discerning purist.",
